<LP>
   GRAND UNION Co. (Wayne, N.J.) -- Robert P. Ferla was named
corporate vice president, training and executive development,
at this supermarket chain. Mr. Ferla, previously vice
president, joined Grand Union in 1958 and reports to Charles
J. Barrett, senior vice president, personnel.
