<LP>
   PROVIDENCE, R.I. -- Bank of New England-Old Colony N.A., a
unit of Bank of New England Corp., said it signed a consent
cease and desist order with the Office of the Comptroller of
the Currency.
   The Bank of New England unit said the consent order deals
