billion from A$3.7 billion, and total income rose 22% to A$10
billion from A$8.2 billion.
   Pearl's income totaled A$3.2 billion in 1989.
   AMP has total reserves of A$5.4 billion, which have risen
from A$4.6 billion in 1988. Reserves total A$13.1 billion
including Pearl's reserves.
